&lt;p&gt;As an amateur, I must spend almost two days for assembling the pc and insstalling softwares (ubuntu, tensorflow and other stuffs).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I end the setup by running a new DRL algorihtm called DDPG in swing-up pendulumn task. The code is written in Python and you can find them in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/pemami4911/deep-rl&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

